## The situation

Maya Patel spent 10 years in leadership development — first as a VP at a Fortune 500, then as an executive coach working with founders, directors, and C-suite leaders. Her clients get results. Her referrals speak for themselves.

But when a referred prospect Googles "Maya Patel coaching" — nothing comes up. No website, no professional presence, no way to learn about her approach before reaching out. In executive coaching, that's a credibility problem.

## The problems

- **No Google presence**: Referred prospects couldn't verify credentials or learn about her approach
- **LinkedIn wasn't enough**: A strong LinkedIn profile doesn't replace a dedicated site with testimonials, programs, and booking
- **No lead capture**: Interested people had no way to engage without committing to a call
- **Competitors looked more established**: Other coaches with polished websites appeared more credible, even with less experience

## What we built

### Credibility-first homepage

The homepage leads with Maya's story, credentials, and the types of leaders she works with. Not a generic coaching template — a specific narrative about her approach and what makes her different.

### Testimonials that sell

Real quotes from leaders who've worked with Maya — specific outcomes, not vague praise. "Maya helped me see patterns I'd been ignoring for years" is more convincing than "Great coach!"

### Free leadership guide

A downloadable guide captures email addresses from people who aren't ready to book but are interested in leadership development. These leads enter a nurture sequence that builds trust over time.

### AI assistant

The chat answers questions about coaching programs, pricing, and Maya's approach. "What's the difference between your executive and team programs?" gets a detailed, helpful answer without Maya spending time on repetitive explanations.

### Direct booking

A clear "Book a Call" button on every page links to a calendar. No friction, no contact forms — just pick a time.

## The results

- **Professional credibility online**: Referred prospects now verify and trust before first contact
- **Lead capture working**: Free guide downloads generating warm leads weekly
- **Testimonials converting**: Prospects read outcomes from similar leaders and book calls
- **Google visibility**: Showing up for "executive coach Greenville" and "leadership coaching SC"

Visit the site: [demo-coach.pages.dev](https://demo-coach.pages.dev)

## Why this matters for your business

If you're a coach, consultant, tutor, or any service professional who relies on trust and credibility — your website is your first impression. Most prospects will Google you before they call you. What they find determines whether they reach out or move on.

